{"tid":2273573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涂謹申承認泛民而家係立法會既作用只得拉布 拖延 發聲","createTime":"2020-11-06T00:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T07:42:05.000Z","uid":13745,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce242923bbe78e16ddb7c0f02aa02bc0fd2c42d4","tid":2273573,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T00:18:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GPYejFSvdCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGPYejFSvdCs&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8jk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=af41f172\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GPYejFSvdCs</a><br />\n<br />\n尋晚議事論事<br />\n涂謹申承認泛民而家係立法會既少數派 作用只得拉布 拖延 發聲 反對 盡量表達憤怒 保皇黨比泛民少市民投票支持但有多數議席 <br />\n而家連 發聲 反對 盡量表達憤怒 都唔俾<br />\n咁係咪證明泛民留低只為保住份工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x01xdtU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx01xdtU.png&h=5584fe36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FubX82g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFubX82g.png&h=915a82da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aaa1212fa6efd98fe9a53c000060884e31fbf033","tid":2273573,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"Btw:「淺藍」轉黃？ 學者與被捕青年<br />\n<br />\n涉及反修例運動被捕人士至今有超過一萬人，其中六成以上是25歲以下的青少年，他們不少都要面對漫長的司法程序，以及經濟上和心理上的壓力。<br />\n一直予人印象為「淺藍」人物的前民主思路聯席召集人<span class=\"red\">宋恩榮，連同他的太太、同為前民主思路聯席秘書長的宋陳寶蓮，以及一班跨學科的專業團隊，幾個月前開始為參與反修例運動被捕的青年，提供社會心理輔導及有關司法程序的支援。政見被指靠近「淺藍」的宋恩榮，如何爭取他們的信任？</span>"},{"pid":"07a025a1d84cfe9892bd5f1bd40bd44a6c19433a","tid":2273573,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7bdfc06126d87ca43b0b5407f3d9223b48565e","tid":2273573,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T02:25:31.000Z","msg":"仲拉到布?"},{"pid":"78e33edf1bb6201